      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Full version-controlled solver with regression test suite covering hemolysis power-law implementation; documented release notes and issue tracking.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R1 used under institutional software quality plan. Hemolysis scalar transport UDF is under Git version control with 47 regression tests. Release validation report on file. Achieved level 4 meets required level 4 for MRL 5 Class III device."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) verification for Navier-Stokes and hemolysis transport equations demonstrating second-order spatial convergence.",
      "rationale": "MMS applied to both the incompressible N-S solver and the power-law hemolysis scalar transport equation. Observed order of accuracy 1.97 ± 0.04 on structured hexahedral meshes. Code verification report archived in project repository. Achieved level 4 satisfies MRL 5 requirement."
    },
    {
